                        <interp inst="t18411213-name-330" type="given" value="OLIVER"></interp>OLIVER CARMICHAEL</persName>
                  </hi>. I am in the employ of Mr. Robert Pugh, who is in partnership with his son—the barge <hi rend="italic">Charlotte</hi> belongs to them, and the coals in it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I picked them up in the dock; they dropped on the ground as they were pitching the sacks.</p>
